{"type": "article", "id": 25923, "title": "可粘壁花盆", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-25T06:59:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 73, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702151014mCEtKwyLoduinsU4.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这个多用途的可粘壁花盆名叫 <a href=\"http://creodes.com/\">Livi</a>，由一个来自美国旧金山的设计团队打造，小巧的设计很容易让人联想到壁虎。花盆有四个支脚，底部采用了纳米微吸胶技术，可以重复粘贴在任何表面，而且不会留下痕迹。如果你参与众筹，单只的早鸟价为 12 美元。你可以在它的 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1982070287/livi-a-new-way-to-experience-plants\">Kickstarter</a> 页面上看到更多的相关信息。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151008KnJp7fcW5r2qBkVt.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.3325\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151008g2eAdkt8wux7vR3M.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021510091cM3ngICKAkrGZy4.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56176471\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151013FMtqI056CEzevZuf.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56029412\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}